description: The trail opens into a wide clearing flooded by moonlight allowed by a break in the massive trees that circle a stucco and timber built building.  A high, thick wall separates the building from a buffer space of broad green lanes that holds back the shadows of the forest.  Giantwomen sentries flank a large gateway offering entry through the wall and to the building within.
